OL,3,CRock n' Roll legend's ashes held in
OL,4,Cunusual place at Download Festival
OL,6,FOne of Download's favourite sons was
OL,7,Fremembered once again when a ceremony
OL,8,Fto enshrine some of his ashes in his
OL,9,Ffavourite slot machine took place.
OL,11,FIan "Lemmy" Kilmister, from Burslem,
OL,12,Fwho made several appearances at the
OL,13,FDownload Festival at Donington Park,
OL,14,Fdied in December 2015, shortly after
OL,15,Fbeing diagnosed with cancer.
OL,26,@sD@EOUsD@KO]
