OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1781550673
OL,3,CRock n' Roll legend's ashes held in
OL,4,Cunusual place at Download Festival
OL,6,FHe played at the festival with
OL,7,FMotorhead in 2005, 2008, 2010, and
OL,8,F2013, when he joined Slash on stage,
OL,9,Fwho played with Saturday night's
OL,10,Fheadliners Guns n' Roses at this
OL,11,Fyear's Download Festival 2026.
OL,13,FThere has been a tribute to him at
OL,14,FDownload since he died, but this year
OL,15,Fwas special with the return of
OL,16,FMotorhead and the Lemmy Forever
OL,17,Finitiative for a special ceremony
OL,18,Fcelebrating the rock icon's life and
OL,19,Flegacy.
OL,26,@oD@DxwxD@Dxw
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/8
