PN,34203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1781550673
OL,3,CRock n' Roll legend's ashes held in
OL,4,Cunusual place at Download Festival
OL,6,FThe ceremony took place at Download's
OL,7,FLemmy's Lounge, where the miniature
OL,8,Fversion of Lemmy's custom urn,
OL,9,Fcontaining a portion of his ashes, was
OL,10,Fplaced in the classic fruit machine,
OL,11,Fwhich was a familiar sight throughout
OL,12,Fmuch of his life on and off the road.
OL,14,FA Lemmy Forever spokesman said, "The
OL,15,Finitiative was created to ensure that
OL,16,FLemmy remains where he always belonged
OL,17,F- among the fans, the music, and the
OL,18,Fplaces that mattered most to him.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1781550673
OL,3,CRock n' Roll legend's ashes held in
OL,4,Cunusual place at Download Festival
OL,6,F"Over the years, portions of his ashes
OL,7,Fhave been placed at locations around
OL,8,Fthe world that held special
OL,9,Fsignificance, allowing fans the
OL,10,Fopportunity to pay their respects and
OL,11,Fcelebrate his extraordinary life.
OL,13,FLong-time friend of Lemmy's, Guns
OL,14,FN'Roses' Duff McKagen, presided over
OL,15,Fthis year's event following the death
OL,16,Fof colleague Phil Campbell earlier
OL,17,Fthis year.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1781550673
OL,3,CRock n' Roll legend's ashes held in
OL,4,Cunusual place at Download Festival
OL,6,FThe Lemmy Forever journey has already
OL,7,Ftaken Lemmy to many of the places he
OL,8,Floved most, including Hellfest in
OL,9,FFrance, Wacken Open Air in Germany,
OL,10,FThe Rainbow Bar & Grill in West
OL,11,FHollywood, Stringfellows in London,
OL,12,FDerbyshire's Bloodstock Open Air, and
OL,13,Fhis hometown of Burslem, Stoke-on-
OL,14,FTrent.
OL,16,F"It remains a responsibility we
OL,17,Fproudly carry," says Motorhead manager
OL,18,FTodd Singerman.
OL,26,@xD@AOUyD@OO]yD@Yxw
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1781550673
OL,3,CRock n' Roll legend's ashes held in
OL,4,Cunusual place at Download Festival
OL,6,F"Not everyone can make the pilgrimage
OL,7,Fto visit Lemmy in Hollywood, so we are
OL,8,Fbringing Lem back to his fans. These
OL,9,Fplaces meant something to him, and
OL,10,Fthey mean something to the people who
OL,11,Floved him.
OL,13,F"It's important that they have
OL,14,Fsomewhere they can come, raise a
OL,15,Fglass, share a story, and spend a
OL,16,Fmoment with him."
OL,26,@xD@QO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/8
