OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1781550673
OL,3,CRock n' Roll legend's ashes held in
OL,4,Cunusual place at Download Festival
OL,6,FFollowing Download, the journey
OL,7,Fcontinues north - on Tuesday 16 June
OL,8,Fat 12 noon, the same ashes enshrined
OL,9,Fat Download will be transported to
OL,10,FManchester Apollo, where another Lemmy
OL,11,FForever ceremony will take place.
OL,13,FIn a fitting tribute to one of
OL,14,FBritain's most beloved rock icons, the
OL,15,Fashes enshrined at Download will make
OL,16,Fthe pilgrimage back to the festival
OL,17,Feach year before returning home to
OL,18,FManchester Apollo, where fans will be
OL,19,Fable to visit Lemmy throughout the
OL,20,Frest of the year.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/8
